snippet.title: HELL SURVIVORS - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2841510/Hell_Survivors

Hell Survivors is a survival roguelite where countless hordes of demons rise from the abyss. Compose a multitude of mighty builds and eradicate waves of nightmare creatures. Will you be able to survive Hell?
